minimum_requirements:
To apply for exchange at the University of Bristol, you should:
1) have completed a minimum of one year’s undergraduate study at NUS;
2) have a GPA of 3.0 out of 4.0 or the equivalent NUS CAP of 3.75 out of 5.0;
3) have a minimum ‘B’ average grade; and no single grade below ‘C’ in the current/intended discipline/major;
4) not be in the graduating semester when they go for exchange at Bristol
